  "Physicians (MDs and DOs) diagnose and treat diseases in patients. This is one of the most well-known biology-related careers, requiring a bachelor's degree, medical school, and residency training.": "",
  "A forensic scientist applies biology to help solve:": "",
  "Math problems — using statistics": "",
  "Crimes — using DNA evidence, blood analysis, and toxicology": "",
  "Computer bugs — debugging software": "",
  "Engineering challenges — designing bridges": "",
  "Forensic scientists use biological evidence — DNA analysis, blood pattern analysis, toxicology, and trace evidence — to help solve crimes and provide evidence for legal proceedings.": "",
